						<summary>

						<p>Stone at the south end of the tank bund.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1509, [Sarvajit], Bhādrapada ba. 30.</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1587 A.D. September 22, Friday.</hi></p>						

						<p>Records the renovation of the tank bund at Kambham, probably by Ghaṇḍi Kūnama Nāyaniṁgāru, and registers gifts of land made to several individuals who seem to have taken part in the renovation work. Mentions Koṇḍaya, Tippaya and Bhogayya.</p>						

						</summary>
